                .accordion-collapse.collapse#collapseMistake2(
                  aria-labelledby='mistake2'
                  data-bs-parent='#mistakesAccordion'
                )
                  .accordion-body
                    p.
                      Scope is about the size of the work itself. People is about coordination complexity. A large data migration (Scope=8) might only need one DBA (People=2). Keep them separate.

              .accordion-item
                h3.accordion-header#mistake3
                  button.accordion-button.collapsed(
                    type='button'
                    data-bs-toggle='collapse'
