                  data-bs-parent='#mistakesAccordion'
                )
                  .accordion-body
                    p.
                      Multiplying Innovation Ã— Scope Ã— People gives you a range of 1-1000. That's too wide. Addition (Innovation + Scope + People) gives you 3-30, which is much more manageable.

